sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor U as User
    participant W as Browser<br/>(verify.fivucsas.com)
    participant API as Identity Core API<br/>(api.fivucsas.com)
    participant BIO as Biometric Service<br/>(internal-only)

    note over U,W: FACE step inside a multi-step login (hosted login / embedded widget)<br/>CLIENT-SIDE-EMBEDDING path -- production default (app.auth.client-side-embedding=true)

    U->>W: look at the camera
    W->>W: getUserMedia capture --<br/>MediaPipe FaceLandmarker (478 pts)
    W->>W: quality pre-gate + ADVISORY passive PAD<br/>(MiniFASNet, onnxruntime-web -- client live-confidence)
    W->>W: compute Facenet512 embedding IN-BROWSER<br/>(onnxruntime-web, L2-normalized 512-d vector)
    note right of W: RAW IMAGE NEVER LEAVES THE DEVICE.<br/>Data minimization: only the irreversible 512-float<br/>vector is sent. Liveness is assured by the<br/>server-verified active Puzzle step + advisory PAD.

    W->>API: POST /api/v1/auth/mfa/step<br/>{sessionToken, method: FACE,<br/>embedding (512 floats), padScore (advisory)}
    API->>API: gates: MFA session valid + not consumed,<br/>account lockout guard (HTTP 423<br/>after 5 failures), rate limit

    API->>BIO: POST /api/v1/verify-embedding<br/>{512-vector}, X-API-Key,<br/>Docker network only
    note over BIO: continues in part (b):<br/>validate dimension, pgvector match, threshold, verdict
